OL,3,CFormer chief constable to face
OL,4,Cmisconduct hearing over workplace sex
OL,5,Callegations
OL,7,FThe former chief constable of
OL,8,FHampshire Police is to face a
OL,9,Fdisciplinary hearing over allegations
OL,10,Fof having sex while on duty and
OL,11,Ffailing to disclose a relationship
OL,12,Fwith another officer.
OL,14,FScott Chilton retired from the top
OL,15,Frole at Hampshire and Isle of Wight
OL,16,FConstabulary in April 2025, after the
OL,17,Fallegations emerged of two workplace
OL,18,Frelationships.
