OL,3,CFormer chief constable to face
OL,4,Cmisconduct hearing over workplace sex
OL,5,Callegations
OL,7,FIt said in a statement: "Our
OL,8,Finvestigation found that the former
OL,9,Fchief constable, who retired while
OL,10,Funder investigation in April, has a
OL,11,Fcase to answer for potential breaches
OL,12,Fof the police standards of
OL,13,Fprofessional behaviour relating to:
OL,14,Fhonesty and integrity; authority,
OL,15,Frespect and courtesy; orders and
OL,16,Finstructions; and discreditable
OL,17,Fconduct.
