OL,5,Callegations
OL,7,FOther allegations are that he "had sex
OL,8,Fwith an officer while on duty before
OL,9,Fbecoming chief constable" and he
OL,10,F"repeatedly and dishonestly denied the
OL,11,Frelationship while he was chief
OL,12,Fconstable to senior figures from both
OL,13,Fthe Hampshire and Isle of Wight police
OL,14,Fand crime commissioner's (PCC) office
OL,15,Fand the force".
OL,17,FIt is also alleged that he "abused his
OL,18,Fposition for a sexual purpose having a
OL,19,Fsexual relationship with an officer
OL,20,Fwhile chief constable and failed to
OL,21,Fdeclare this relationship".
